title: Splunk: System messages
agents: splunk
catalog: app/splunk
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the occurance of system messages in splunk. It outputs
 the last worst state in the service details and an overview of all messages in
 the long output section.

 Please note that you have to clear such messages within Splunk.

inventory:
 One service for will be created

